  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span dir=\"ltr\">An antidote kit contained a variety of wide-spectrum antidote injectors that were designed to neutralize most commonly encountered poisons.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">A kit has two Syringes (Uses).</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">As an action, you can administer a Syringe of the kit to cure a target of one poison of D-Rank or lower, affecting them or to give them advantage on saving throws against a Poison or poisoned condition of up to 1 rank higher for 1 hour.</span></p><p></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Cures D Rank Poisons</span></p>",
